author: The Critical Drinker
description:
This week has been filled with Even Stranger Things, from the Conformity Gate conspiracy theory that turned out to be nothing more than Desperate Cope, to the new teasers for Avengers Doomsday and news that Kathleen Kennedy is retiring (again). Join me, MauLer, Jeremy from Geeks+Gamers, Reaper and Metal as we talk about it all. 

Subscribe to Jeremy: https://www.youtube.com/@DDayCobra
Subscribe to Reaper: https://www.youtube.com/@RealReaper
Subscribe to Metal: https://www.youtube.com/@Metalsforge
title: Open Bar #170 - Doomsday Doomed, Kennedy Retiring, Conformity Gate Cope
